{"tid":2415384,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★新股IPO】京東物流值不值得認購？ 連虧13年！","createTime":"2021-02-20T07:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T11:37:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dec1b04c200c3b55eb6487698f3d2ada6290ddff","tid":2415384,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"京東物流前身為京東旗下內部物流服務部門，2017年京東物流宣布獨立營運，成立京東物流子集團。京東創辦人劉強東早年曾因砸重金自建物流被質疑，因倉庫、人力成本投資龐大，重資產模式與京東互聯網企業定位格格不入，京東物流的投資負擔曾經拖累京東業績多年。<br />\n<br />\n劉強東當年力排眾議自建物流，據報是要解決快遞容易遺失、延誤、包裝破損等問題，「為用戶體驗燒錢，我覺得值得」。他曾經在2019年4月發內部信，稱京東物流2018年的虧損就超過23億元（人民幣，下同），<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>已經第十二年錄得虧損。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2881671/【新股IPO】京東物流值不值得認購？%20%20%20連虧13年、第4家京東系上市公司?mtc=40001&amp;srkw=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2881671%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC%EF%BC%9F%2520%2520%2520%E9%80%A3%E8%99%A713%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%81%E7%AC%AC4%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1%E7%B3%BB%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%3Fmtc%3D40001%26srkw%3D&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0e306628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2881671/【新股IPO】京東物流值不值得認購？%20%20%20連虧13年、第4家京東系上市公司?mtc=40001&amp;srkw=</a>"},{"pid":"8eadd2c3bc003a3b3e496790fe11cec2760efce3","tid":2415384,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542af65f621048e8e275cfe0352528c62808